\mt1 Jems Osirizir Ak…®nafarim 
\is1 Akar Faragha Zuim 
\ip Jems…®n Ak…®nafarim akar aghuir av…®riba iti. Jems God…®n gumazamiziba arazir aghuibar g…®n mangasa, egha men sure damuasa akar aghuir av…®rir kaba osiri. A gumazamizibar akurvaght…® me n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozim iniva, egh derav…®ra an akam g…®n…®ghn…®ghasa an akar is…®n zuir av…®riba osiri. 
\ip Jems m…®gh…®ghav…®ra m…®g…®a ghaze, gumazir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Iesus…®n itim, a pura ikian kogham. Puvat…®. An arazir aghuibar igharaz darazir amuam, eght…® arazir kam kamagh…®n men akagham, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. 
\c 1  
\ms1 E os…®mt…®zibar tuivigh gavgavigh…®va egh derav…®ra God ko ikiam 
\mr (Sapta 1:1-18) 
\p  
\v 1 K…® Jems, k…® God ko Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n ingangarir gumazim. K…® ia 12 plan Israel…®n itir anababa bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Kar ia gumazamizir uan nguibam ategha ghua kantrin igharazibar iti. K…® dughiar aghuim ia gan…®di.\f + \ft (1:1) 12 plan Israel…®n anabar kaba, da God…®n gumazamizir nguazir kam…®n bar an tibar ababanim gami.\f* 
\s1 Os…®mt…®ziba, da gavgavim e gan…®di 
\p  
\v 2-3 Nan adarasi, ia fo, os…®mt…®zir ia bativiba, da ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar amut…® ia tuivigh gavgavigh egh os…®mt…®ziba ater mangv…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ia bativt…®ma ia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, ia bar akongegh.  
\v 4 Egh ia zurara tuivigh gavgavigh egh os…®mt…®ziba ater. Eght…® arazir kam ian ik…® gavgavigh mamagh…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®n ia derav…®ra ik…®va, egh ia God…®n bizitam…®n oteveghan kogham. Puvat…®. Ian araziba bar deragh…®va, egh ia God…®n arazibar aghung mang…® gumazamizir aruabar m…®n otogham. 
\s1 Gumazim n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar otevegh, a God ko m…®k…®m 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® ian tav n…®ghn…®zir aghuibar otevegh, a God…®n azangs…®ght…®ma, God a dan…®ngam. God pura biziba gumaziba bar me gan…®di, an atarir puvat…®. Kar God…®n bizibar anogorozir puvat…®zim, me an azangs…®zima a me dan…®ngasa bar ifonge.  
\v 6 Eght…® gumazim God ko m…®k…®m…®va, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ik…®, a n…®ghn…®zir pumuning ikian mark…®, egh suam, ‚ÄúGod ti bizitam na danigam, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù E fo, gumazim n…®ghn…®zir pumuning iti, a mati am…®nim ongarim givav amadima a pura tintinibar d…®kafi.  
\v 7 Gumazir kam kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, Ekiam bizitam a danigham. Puvat…®.  
\v 8 Gumazir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zim bar tuiraghr…®z…®, an arazir an amiba, da tuavir vam…®ran itir puvat…®. 
\s1 Jems onganaraziba ko gumazir bizir av…®riba itiba akam me gan…®di 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazim, onganarazibagh amua iti, a God…®n damazim…®n ziar ekiam iti. Kamagh…®n, a bar akuegh ik…®.  
\v 10 Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim itir gumazim, bizir av…®riba iti, a fo, God g…®n a d…®kab…®raght…® an ak…®marir atiabar m…®n aremegham. Kamagh…®n, a uaghan bar akuegh ik…®.  
\v 11 E fo, aruem anaga pamtem gara temem gisiraz…®ma a m…®d…®i. Ez…® temem…®n ak…®marir aghuiba suaghira, egha dar ganganim bar ikufi. Ez…® kamagh…®ra gumazir bizir av…®riba itim, a uan ingangarim damuv…®ra ik…®va an tong…®n aremegham. 
\s1 God arazir aghuibar e gami, egha arazir kurabar amuasa e ab…®rir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 12 Gumazim os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va, egh uaghan os…®mt…®ziba bar dar aven tugh gavgavigh, uan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ateghan koght…®, God ivezir aghuim a dan…®ngt…®ma a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim iniam. Ivezir aghuir kam, God akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, gumazir bar a gifongeziba, a me dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, gumazir kam bar akongegh. 
\p  
\v 13 Kamagh…®n gumazitam bizitam an navim ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damigham, a kamagh…®n m…®k…®man mark…®, ‚ÄúGod na ab…®raz…®ma k…® arazir kam gami.‚Äù Puvat…®. E fo, gumazitam God ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damighan kogham, eght…® God gumazitam ab…®raght…®ma an arazir kuratam damighan kogham.  
\v 14 Ez…® en navir kuraba vaghvagha arazir kurabar amuasa e gifarava e apezeperava e gakaghori.  
\v 15 Ez…® navir d…®gavir kam, a mati amizim navim adai, egha g…®n arazir kuram gamiz…®ma an oto, mati borim…®n m…®n a bate. Ez…® arazir kuram ghua ekevezir dughiam, an ovevem gamiz…®ma an oto.  
\v 16 Nan adarasi, ia gumazitam ateght…® a ia gifaran mark…®.  
\v 17 Bizir bar aghuir e isiba, ko bizir ikuvir puvat…®ziba, da bar God…®n Nguibam…®n p…®n izaghiri. God Afeziam a biziba bar overiam dar ingari, a bizir aghuir kaba e bagha da amadi da izaghiri. Ez…® Afeziar kam a uan araziba raghrazir puvat…®. A bizitam…®n nedazim…®n m…®n aruem a gisiraz…® an otevegha ruarazir puvat…®. A kamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 18 God kamagh sua, a biziba bar dar ingari, egha e gamiz…® e bar dar faragh mangam. Kamagh…®n God uab…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghuava en Afeziam…®n oto, a uan guiz…®n akam…®n e gamiz…®ma e otifi. 
\ms1 E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim guizbang…®ra God…®n ik…®va, e uaghan arazir aghuibar amuam 
\mr (Sapta 1:19-5:6) 
\s1 E akar aghuim baragh, egh uaghan an g…®n mangam 
\p  
\v 19 Nan adarasi, ia derav…®ra bizir kam g…®fogh. Ia bar zuam…®ra kuariba ar…®gh akaba baragh, egh ia zuam…®ra m…®k…®man mark…®, egh zuam…®ra ataran mark…®.  
\v 20 E fo, atarir gumazim, God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh amima da otivir puvat…®.  
\v 21 Kamagh…®n amiz…® ia bar arazir m…®z…®r…®ziba ko arazir kurar otiviba, ia bar ada munamadagh. Egh ia bar uari d…®kab…®ragh egh akar God ian navir averiam…®n d…®karazim inigh. Eght…® akar kam ian akuragham.  
\v 22 Egh akar ia inizir kam, ia an m…®rara mang…®. Ia puram orarazir k…®nim damuan mark…®. Puvat…®. Ia pura orarazir k…®nim…®n damuam, kamagh…®n ia uarira uarigh ifari.  
\v 23 Gumazitam pura God…®n akam baregh, egh an g…®n zuir puvat…®, a mati gumazim ganganim…®n uan guam…®n gari.  
\v 24 Egha a derav…®ra uan guam…®n ganigha, egha ua ghugha ok…®n…®ghn…®ki, an guam manmagh…®ra gari.  
\v 25 Ez…® God…®n akar bar derav…®ra itim e gamima e f…®riagh…®r…®. Eght…® gumazitam derav…®ra akar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, egh pura akam baragh zuam…®ra ok…®n…®gh…®n…®ghan kogh, egh bar an akam…®n g…®n mang…®t…®, gumazir kam, God an ingangaribar amut…® da bar derav…®ram otivam. 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® gumazitam kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n gumazir bar aghuim, egha guizbang…®ra an ziam fe,‚Äù egha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar aghuibar uan m…®zem…®n dav geir puvat…®, kamagh…®n a uab…®ra uab…® gifari. Ez…® kamagh…®n an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko God…®n ziam fer arazim pura bizim.  
\v 27 Guizbang…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir God Afeziam…®n damazim…®n deragha os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zim, a kamak…®n: E borir ameboghfeziaba ovengezibar akurvagh…®va, amizir odiarir men paba ovengeziba sarama akurvagh, egh men os…®mt…®ziba ateram. Ez…® uaghan bizir mam, e uari uan daroriba derav…®ra dar ganam, eght…® nguazir kam…®n araziba e damut…® e God…®n damazim…®n m…®zeghan kogham. 
\c 2  
\s1 E arazir amir vam…®ran, bar gumazibar amuam 
\p  
\v 1 Nan adarasi, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n iti, a bizir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n itibar Ekiam. Ia gumazir ziaba itiba derav…®ra me damu egh gumazir ziaba puvat…®ziba ak…®rim ragh me gasan mark…®. Ia amir arazir vam…®ran bar me damu.  
\v 2 Eght…® gumazitam kurukazir bar aghuim damigh, egh gol…®n ring uan dafarim dat…®gh, egh God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven mangam, eght…® gumazir onganarazim korotiar b…®b…®zibar kurukegh egh uaghan God ko m…®geir d…®penim…®n aven mangam,  
\v 3 eght…® kurukazir bar aghuim gamizir gumazim ia derav…®ra a damuva, egh a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúAruam, n…® iz…® dabirabir aghuir kam daperagh,‚Äù egh ia onganarazibagh amir gumazim kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúN…® munagh tugh,‚Äù o ‚ÄúN…® nan dagarimning borogh…®n magh vazim daperagh,‚Äù  
\v 4 ia arazir kam kamagh…®n a gami. Mati ia uan n…®ghn…®zibar aven igharazi darazi ab…®gha men araziba tuis…®si. Egha ia derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gha gumazibar araziba arazir vam…®ran me tuis…®zir pu. Puvat…®. Ia mati jasbar m…®n otivigha n…®ghn…®zir bar kurabar gumaziba tuis…®si. 
\p  
\v 5 Nan adarasi, ia oragh. Nguazim…®n itir gumazibar damazibar itir gumazir onganaraziba, gumazir kaba God me am…®sevegha ghaze, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim…®n iti. A fom…®ra gumazamizir bar a gifongeziba bagha akam ak…®ra ghaze, a bar me gativagh men ganam. Kamagh…®n a gumazir onganarazir kaba m…®sevegha ghaze, me God Bizibagh Ativamin Dughiam…®n aven ikiam.  
\v 6 Ez…® ia akar aghums…®ziba onganarazibagh an…®di. Ia n…®ghn…®gh! Tina ia d…®kab…®ra egha os…®mt…®ziba ia gar…®si, egha ia m…®k…®rvagha kotiabar zui? Kar gumazir dag…®aba bar iz…®vaziba arazir kabagh ami.  
\v 7 Ez…® God Iesus…®n ziar aghuim ia gat…®, ez…® tina ziar aghuir kam gas…®ghas…®si? Dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazir kabara. 
\p  
\v 8 God en atrivir ekiam, egha an Ak…®nafarim…®n an akar ekiar mam e ganiga ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uab…® uab…® gifongez…® mogh…®n, n…® igharaz darazigh ifongegh.‚Äù Egh ia akar kam guizbang…®ra a baragh an g…®n mang…®, kamagh…®n ia arazir aghuim damuam.  
\v 9 Ez…® ia arazir aghuim gumazir mam gamua egha igharazim ak…®rim a gasara, kamagh…®n ia arazir kuram gami. Ez…® Moses Osirizir Araziba kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia an akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 10 Eght…® gumazitam Moses Osirizir Araziba bar dar g…®n mang…®va, egh arazir vam…®ra abigh…®va, kamagh…®n an arazir kuram gami. A mati gumazir Moses Osirizir Araziba bar da b…®ghizim.  
\v 11 E fo, God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuan mark…®.‚Äù Egha a uaghan kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazibav soght…®ma me ar…®m…®gh…®ran mark…®.‚Äù Eght…® ia poroghamiba uari bakeir arazim damuan kogh…®va, egh ia gumazir mam m…®sueght…® an aremegham, kamagh…®n ia Moses Osirizir Araziba ab…®zir gumazibar otifi. 
\p  
\v 12 Ia fo, God…®n arazim en arazir kuram…®n gavgavim a g…®vagham, egh…®va e damut…® e f…®righr…®gham. Egh g…®n God uan arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va egh en araziba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n, ia gumazir God…®n Arazim…®n apengan itibar akaba ko araziba zurara dar amu.  
\v 13 E fo, gumazitam igharaz darazir apangkuvir puvat…®, eght…® God kotiam…®n a tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n God uaghan an apangkuvighan kogham. Ez…® gumazim igharaz darazir apangkufi, God…®n kotiam…®n a tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n a God…®n apangkuvim…®n ganam. 
\s1 N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim arazir aghuim sara zuir puvat…®, a pura bizim 
\p  
\v 14 Nan adarasi, gumazitam suam, ‚ÄúK…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n iti,‚Äù egha an arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim pura bizim. Kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam an akuragham, o puvat…®? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 15 Ez…® Krais…®n adarazir aveghbuatam o buaramizitam, korotiaba ko dagheba puvat…®,  
\v 16 eght…® ian tav kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúN…® navir am…®r…®zim…®n ik…®. N…® mang…®va inim ikegh…®va uan m…®karzim avaragh. Egh mang…® dagher av…®ribar am…®va egh navim iz…®fagh.‚Äù Eght…® akar kam manmagh…®n an akuragham? Ia uari korotiaba ko dagheba an akurvaght…®ma a derav…®ra ikiam.  
\v 17 Ez…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim…®n arazim uaghan kamagh…®ra ghu. N…®ghn…®zir gavgavim pura ikia, egha arazir aghuiba sara zuir puvat…®, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam, an aremez…® mogh…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 18 Tav kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄúGumazir maba n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba iti, ez…® gumazir igharaziba arazir aghuibagh ami.‚Äù K…® kamagh…®n n…®n akam ikaragham, ‚ÄúN…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia egha arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n k…® manmagh…®n n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim g…®fogham? K…® arazir aghuibar amuam, eght…® arazir kabara nan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n akagham.‚Äù  
\v 19 N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n ikia ghaze, ‚ÄúGod…®n vam…®ra iti.‚Äù A dera. Duar kuraba uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavir kam ikia, egha agoa atiati. 
\p  
\v 20 N…® gumazir onganim! N…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra ikiava egha arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n n…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim a pura bizim. N…® ti akar kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa, o? Ia oragh.  
\v 21 Fom…®ra en ovavim Abraham uan otarim Aisak isa ofa gamir danganim…®n anet…®gha egha God…®n ofa gami mogh…®n a gami. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n God an arazim…®n ganigha egha Abraham m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.  
\v 22 Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Abraham…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ko an arazir aghuim vorogh…®ra ghu. Ez…® arazir aghuir kam bar an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gamima a guizbang…®ra gavgafi.  
\v 23 God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAbraham, a n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n itima, God an ganigha a d…®bora ghaze, a nan damazim…®n derazir gumazim.‚Äù Egha God kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúNan roroam.‚Äù Ez…® akar kam…®n m…®ngarim, God a gamiz…®ma me Ak…®nafarim…®n an osiri, Abraham uan otarim Aisak gamizir dughiam…®n arazir kam, a bar azenan oto.  
\v 24 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia fo, gumazitam pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, God, ‚Äúgumazir God…®n damazim…®n derazim‚Äù a d…®borir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. A gumazir arazir aghuim gamim g…®n…®ghn…®gha, egha an n…®ghn…®zir gavgavimra g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®, egha bizir kam bagha God a d…®bora ghaze, a nan damazim…®n dera. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® tuavir kamra, arazir kurabagh amir amizim Rahap, moga garir gumazir Josua amadazimning…®n akuragha aning amadaz…®ma aning tuavir igharazim…®n ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma God amizir kam m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan damazim…®n dera.  
\v 26 E fo, gumazim…®n duam an m…®karzim…®n averiam…®n itir puvat…®, an aremegha g…®fa. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, gumazim pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti, egha an arazir aghuibagh amir puvat…®, kamagh…®n gumazir kam…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an aremez…® mogh…®n iti. 
\c 3  
\s1 E uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba derav…®ra dar ganam 
\p  
\v 1 Nan adarasi, dughiar God gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®gham…®n, e gumazir, gumazamizibar sure gamir ingangarim iniziba, God bar derav…®ra en ingangariba tuis…®gham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ian tarazira God ifongezir arazibar gumazamizibar sure damuamin ingangarim inighan kogham.  
\v 2 Dughiar av…®ribar e bizir vabara damuasa n…®ghn…®gha, egha e paza dagh ami. Bizir kaba bar e batifi. Ez…® gumazitam dughiatam…®n paza m…®geir puvat…®, a bar gumazir aghuimra, egha a uan m…®karzim bar derav…®ra an gari. 
\p  
\v 3 E ain…®n otevim isava hoz…®n akam gighufa, eght…® ain…®n otevir kam a damut…® a en akam baragh…®va derav…®ra mangam. Ez…® arazir kam…®n e bar derav…®ra men gant…®, me en g…®n mangam.  
\v 4 Ez…® ia kuribagh n…®ghn…®gh. Kuriba bizir bar ekiaba, ez…® am…®nir ekiar gavgaviba dagh ivaima, da ongarim gis…®n ivemari. Ez…® dar stiaba bar sufi. Ez…® dar stian suizir gumazim managh mang…®s…® ifongegha, egha a stia gighavk…®rima kurim tuavir kepten ifongezim…®n zui.  
\v 5 Ez…® kamagh…®ra, m…®zem uaghan bar suvigha en m…®karzim…®n aven iti. Egha a zurara bar puv…®ra ifaghati, egha uab…® uan ziam puv a fe. E fo, avir muziarimra avir ekiam damight…® a bar ekevegh…®va egh ruarim…®n isit…®ma temeba bar isigham!  
\v 6 Ez…® m…®zem uaghan mati avim, egha a en m…®karzir otevir muziarir mam. Egha a uaghan arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami da otifi. A en m…®karzibagh amima da m…®ze, egha arazir kurar av…®ribagh amima da en ik…®r…®m…®ribar otifi, mati avir m…®zariar ekiaba. Avir kam a uab…® hel…®n avim. 
\p  
\v 7 E fo, gumaziba as…®zir atiaba bar mogh…®ra da isava dar dai, kuaraziba ko as…®zir davaragharuiba ko ongarim…®n aven itir biziba bar. Egha me bizir kabar dava egha me dar gari da men apengan iti.  
\v 8 Gumazitam uab…® uan m…®zem damight…®ma an an apengan ikeghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. En m…®zeba zurara akar kurabav gei. Mati imezir kuraba gumazibagh amima da ariaghiri, da en akabagh iz…®fa. 
\p  
\v 9 E uan m…®zebar Ekiam…®n ziam fe, a en Afeziam. God gumazamizibar ingariz…®ma me an m…®rara otifi, ez…® e uan m…®zebar e akar kurabav g…®ava gumazamizir igharazibagh as…®ghas…®si.  
\v 10 Ekiam fer akaba ko akar kuraba, aning v…®rara m…®zer vam…®ram otifi. Nan adarasi, arazir kam a ikian kogham.  
\v 11 Mozir d…®patam, d…®par aghuim ko ongarir pam, uaning veregh ikiam ti? Puvat…®!  
\v 12 Nan adarasi, figh…®n temem oliv…®n temem…®n m…®n bam, o? Puvat…®! O wain…®n temem a figh…®n temem m…®n bam, o? Puvat…®! Kamagh…®ra d…®par apir aghuim ongarir d…®pam ko ik…®va otivan kogham. 
\s1 Gumazim God…®n izezir fofozim ik…®va, an arazir aghuibar amuam 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazitam ian tong…®n fofozir aghuim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuim iti, o? Kamagh…®n amir gumazitam ik…®va, an dabirabim bar deragh. A fofozir aghuim…®n arazibar g…®n mang…®va gumazibar asughasugh…®va egh uab…® uan ziam fan kogham. Eght…® gumaziba an arazir aghuir an amibar ganam.  
\v 14 Eght…® ia igharaz darazi navir bar kuraba men ik…®va, egh zurara uan ziaba f…®s…® tuaviba buriam, kamagh…®n ia uan fofozim ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba bagh bar akueghan mark…®. Ia ifaragh egh uan arazibar guiz…®n akam d…®kab…®raghan mark…®.  
\v 15 Ez…® fofozir kam a God…®n Nguibam…®n ikegha izir pu. Puvat…®, kar nguazir kam…®n bizim. A navir ghurim…®n oto. Ez…® Satan, an afeziam.  
\v 16 Ia oragh. Gumaziba navir kuraba gumazir igharazibar iti, egha me zurara uan ziaba fasa tuaviba buri, gumazir kaba me navir vam…®ra itir puvat…®. Me arazir kuraba bar dagh ami. 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir fofozir aghuir God…®n Nguibam…®n izezim iniziba, me arazir kabagh ami: Faragha zuir arazim, me zurara n…®ghn…®zir zuezibar g…®n zui. Egha me igharaz darazi ko navir vam…®ran iti, egha gumazibar asughasusi. Egha me gumazir igharazibar akaba barasi. Me igharaz darazir apangkuva egha arazir aghuibar me gami. Egha me arazir kamra gumaziba bar me gami. Egha me arazir aghuibar g…®n ghua ifarir puvat…®. Me bar guizbang…®ra dar g…®n zui.  
\v 18 Ez…® kamagh…®n e navir vam…®ra iti, kar mati e dagher anabam akara. Ez…® navir vam…®ran arazim…®n tuavim…®n, arazir aghuiba en dabirabim…®n otifi, mati dagher aghuiba azenim…®n aghui. 
\c 4  
\s1 Gumazir nguazim…®n arazibagh ifongezim, a God…®n apanim 
\p  
\v 1 Bizir m…®ngarir manaba adariba ko m…®dorozibagh amima da ian tong…®n otifi? M…®karzim…®n agorogem…®n araziba ian navibar iti, egha da ian m…®karzibar aven ikia ia ko m…®sosi, kamagh…®n amiz…®ma arazir kam…®n da akam adariba ko m…®dorozibagh amima da otifi. Ti kamagh…®n puvat…®, o?  
\v 2 Ia biziba iniasa bar ifonge, egha ia da isir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia gumazibav sozima da ariagh…®ri. Ia biziba iniasa dagh agoava, egha ia da isir puvat…®. Egha ia puv atara m…®sosi. Ia biziba iniasa ia God ko m…®geir puvat…®, ez…® bizir kam bagha ia da isir puvat…®.  
\v 3 Egha ia biziba iniasa God ko m…®gei, egha ia da isir puvat…®. Ian n…®ghn…®ziba derazir puvat…®z…®ma ia God ko m…®gei. Ia bizir ian m…®karzim…®n agorogem itiba bagha n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n, ia biziba isir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 4 Ia God ataki, mati amizim uan pam ategha ghua gumazir igharaziba isava akui. Ia orakigh! Gumazim nguazim…®n arazibagh ifonge, a God…®n apanim. Ez…® ia ti bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®, o? Gumazim nguazim…®n arazibar namakam gami, a God…®n apanim…®n oto.  
\v 5 God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDuar God en navir averiabagh at…®zir kam, e God uab…®n apengara ikiasa a bar ifonge.‚Äù Ia ti ghaze, akar kam ti pura bizim? Puvat…®.  
\v 6 God en apangkuvav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúGod zurara gumazir uan ziaba feba a me d…®kab…®ri, 
\q2 egha gumazir uan ziaba d…®kab…®riba God men apangkuva 
\q3 egha bar derav…®ra me gami.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia uari d…®kab…®ragh egh God…®n apengan ik…®. Ia Satan munasaraght…®, eght…® a ia ategh ar…®mang…®gham.  
\v 8 Eght…® ia God…®n borogh…®ra mang…®t…®, God ian borogh…®ra izam. Ia gumazir kuraba, ian naviba bar zuegh ik…®, mati gumazim uan dafariba ruez…® da bar zue. Ez…® ia gumazir n…®ghn…®zir pumuning itiba, ia n…®ghn…®zir kurar ian navim…®n itiba da atakigh.  
\v 9 Ia naviba bar osemegh egh pamtem arang…®va aziam. Ia gumazir dat…®r…®gh…®n atiba, ia uan akazim ategh, egh ia arang. Ia gumazir bar akongeziba, ia uan agoroger kam ategh, naviba bar osemegh azi ik…®.  
\v 10 Ia God…®n damazim…®n bar uari d…®kab…®ragh ik…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, God ia fegham. 
\s1 E akaba igharaz darazigh asan kogham 
\p  
\v 11 Nan adarasi, ia God…®n gumazamizir igharaziba akar kurabar me m…®k…®man mark…®. Gumazim akar kuram…®n igharazitav m…®keme, o akam a gasi, an akar kuram…®n Moses Osirizir Arazibav gei, egha a Moses Osirizir Araziba iria. Ez…® ia Moses Osirizir Araziba iria, ia mati gumazim Moses Osirizir Arazibar apengan itir pu. Puvat…®. Ia mati jas…®n m…®n oto.\f + \ft (4:11) Moses Osirizir Arazibar aven itir akar otevir kam, Jems ti vez…®n kam…®n a gin…®r…®. Kar akar Wok Pris 19:18 ko Jems 2:8…®n itim.\f* 
\v 12 God uab…®ra Moses Osirizir Araziba an…®di, egha a uab…®ra jas. A uab…®ra gumazamizibar akurvagham, o me gas…®ghas…®gham. Kamagh…®n ia te, ia jas…®n m…®n gumazamizir igharaziba tuis…®si? 
\s1 E kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, Ekiam ifueght…®ma, e bizir e n…®ghn…®zibar amuam 
\p  
\v 13 Ia oragh, ian tina suam, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n, o gurumzaraghan e nguibar ekiar mam…®n mang…®gh…®va dag…®ar ingangarim azenir vam…®ran a damigham. Egh arazir kam…®n e dag…®ar av…®riba iniam.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ia zurara kamagh…®n m…®g…®a, egha ia fozir puvat…®, bizir manam gurumzaraghan otivam. Ian ik…®r…®m…®rim mati m…®gharim, a dughiar otevimra ikegh egh bar g…®vagham.  
\v 15 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kamagh…®n m…®k…®m, ‚ÄúEkiam ifueght…®ma, e angamra ik…®va, egh bizir e n…®ghn…®zibar amuam.‚Äù  
\v 16 Ez…® ian arazir ia dat…®r…®gh…®n amim, ia uari uan ziaba fava egha ingangarir ekiabar amuasa dar gun m…®gei. Ia uari fer akar kam, a bar ikufi.  
\v 17 Ia derav…®ra n…®ghn…®gh! Ia arazir aghuir damuamin tam g…®fogh, egh ia a damuan kogh…®va, kamagh…®n ia arazir kuram gami. 
\c 5  
\s1 Gumazir bizir av…®riba itiba me ivezir kuram iniam 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir av…®riba itir gumaziba, k…® akam ia m…®k…®masa ifonge. Ia oragh! Ia os…®mt…®zir ekiar ia bativamibagh n…®ghn…®gh, egh ia pamtem d…®m…®va arang ik…®.  
\v 2 Ian bizir aghuiba da bar kuvigham. Eght…® ian korotiaba barareba dar ghoregham.  
\v 3 Eght…® ian gol ko silvaba bar m…®ghovegham, eght…® m…®z…®r…®zir kam ian arazir kurabar amight…® da azenim giregham. Eght…® m…®z…®r…®zir kam avim…®n m…®n ian m…®karzibar isiam. Ekiam izamin dughiam bar rogh…®ra izi, ez…® ia pura biziba ko dag…®aba akuvaz…®ma da iti.\f + \ft (5:3) God gumazamizibar arazibar tuis…®ghamin dughiam…®n, a dag…®ar av…®riba itir gumazibar bizir aghuibar gan…®va da tuis…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. A men arazibar gan…®va da tuis…®gham. Gumazir kaba, bizir bar kuvigham dar suiki, ez…® bizir kam en aka ghaze, me nguazim…®n itir dughiam…®n me arazir aghuim gamir puvat…®. Ez…® avir kam…®n akam ghaze, me ivezir kuram iniam.\f* 
\v 4 Ia derav…®ra oragh, ingangarir gumaziba ian azenibar dagheba isi, ez…® ia me gifaragha egha men ivezir mabar anogoroke. Ez…® ingangarir gumazir kaba me uan ivezibagh n…®ghn…®gha egha God…®n d…®a ghaze, a ian arazir kuraba ikarvagham. Ez…® ingangarir gumazibar d…®mdiam, Ekiar Bar Gavgavim Itim, a baraki.  
\v 5 Ez…® dughiar ia nguazir kam…®n itim, ia bizir aghuir av…®riba isava egha ia bar akuegha iti. Egha ia dagher av…®riba apava bar ekefe. Ez…® God ia m…®soght…® ia ar…®m…®gh…®ramin dughiam, an otogha g…®fa.  
\v 6 Ia gumazir aghuibar kotim gamigha egha me m…®soghez…®ma me ariagh…®re. Ez…® me ian gavgavim munamadir puvat…®, egha ia ikarvagha ia m…®soghezir puvat…®. 
\ms1 Ia gavgavigh ik…®va egh God ko m…®k…®m, egh Ekiam m…®zuamt…® a ua izam 
\mr (Sapta 5:7-20) 
\s1 E gavgavigh ik…®va egh os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va egh Ekiam m…®zuamt…® a izam 
\p  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, nan adarasi, ia tuivigh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba ater…®va egh Ekiam m…®zuamt…® a ua izam. Ia fo, gumazir azenim itim, a dagher aghuiba an azenim…®n aghungasa an adav zuai. Egha a gavgavim uan navim gan…®ga egha aghumra ikiava amozim ko aruem m…®zuai, aning uan ingangarim faragh a damuam. Eght…® a g…®n dagheba iniam.  
\v 8 Ez…® ia uaghan gavgavim uan navibar an…®ng…®va egh aghumra ik…®va egh os…®mt…®zir ia bativim ater. Ia fo, Ekiam Izamin Dughiam a bar rogh…®ra ize. Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma ia tuivigh gavgavigh ik…®.  
\v 9 Nan adarasi, ia God…®n gumazamizir igharazibar atar…®va egh ak…®ribar me m…®k…®man mark…®. Ia fo, ia kamagh…®n damut…®ma, God jas…®n m…®n otogh…®va ian arazir kuraba tuis…®gham. Ia oragh, jas…®n kam a tiar akam…®n tughav iti!  
\v 10 Nan adarasi, ia fom…®ra God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir Ekiam…®n ziam…®n akam akuniziba, ia me g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Apaniba arazir kurabar me gami, ez…® me tuivigha gavgavigha os…®mt…®zir kam ateri. Ia men arazir kam inigh, egh men g…®n mang…®.  
\v 11 Ia oragh. E ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir tuivigha gavgavigha os…®mt…®ziba ateriba, me bar akuegha egha derav…®ra iti.‚Äù Ia Jop…®n eghaghanim g…®fo, a tugha gavgavigha os…®mt…®zir a batoziba a bar da ateri. Ez…® ia fo, Ekiam g…®n bar arazir aghuim…®n a gami. E bar fo, Ekiam en apangkuvav…®ra iti, egha zurara bar derav…®ra e gami. 
\s1 E guizbang…®ra p…®n dar…®gh m…®k…®man kogham 
\p  
\v 12 Nan adarasi, e damuamin bizir faragha zuim, a kamak…®n. Dughiar ia akar d…®k…®r…®zim damuamim, ia pura God…®n Nguibam…®n ziam d…®ponan mark…®, egh guizbang…®ra dar…®gh nguazim o bizir igharazim d…®ponan mark…®. Egh ia pura suam, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra bizir kam damuam.‚Äù Egh suam, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra bizir kam damuan kogham.‚Äù Egh ia uan akam…®n g…®n mang…®. Ia m…®k…®m…®va guizbang…®ra p…®n d…®boroght…®, eght…® God ivezir kuram ia danigam. 
\s1 God…®n damazim…®n derazir gumazim, a God ko m…®gei, an azangs…®zim bar gavgavir ekiam iti 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® ian tav ti os…®mt…®zim ateri? Kamagh…®n a God ko m…®k…®m. Ez…® ian tav ti bar akonge? An Ekiam…®n ziam fer ighiabar amu.  
\v 14 Ez…® ian tav ti arei? A Krais…®n adarazir gumazir dapanibar diaght…®ma, me iz…®, a bagh God ko m…®k…®m…®va, egh Ekiam…®n ziam…®n me borem an m…®karzim gingegh.  
\v 15 Egh me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ik…®va God ko m…®k…®mt…®ma, eght…® azangs…®zir kaba an akurvagh a damight…®ma, a ghuamaghegham. Ekiam ar…®mariar gumazir kam uam a fegham. Eght…® an amizir arazir kuraba, Ekiam da g…®n amadagham.  
\v 16 Kamagh…®n amiz…®ma, ia vaghvagh uan arazir kurabar gun God…®n gumazamizir igharazibav k…®m. Eght…® God ian akurvaghs…®, ia uari bagh God ko m…®k…®mt…®ma, eght…® God ia damight…®ma ia ua deragham. Ez…® gumazir God…®n damazim…®n deraghav…®ra itim God ko m…®gei, an azangs…®zim bar gavgavir ekiam iti, eght…® a igharaz darazir akurvagham. 
\p  
\v 17 Elaija en m…®n garir gumazim. Egha a pamtem God ko m…®kemegha ghaze, amozim…®n izan kogham. Ez…® God amozim t…®vaz…®ma amozim azenir 3 pla ko iakinir 6 plan nguazim…®n izezir pu.\f + \ft (5:17) Elaija, a fom…®ra itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim.\f* 
\v 18 Egha a g…®n ua God ko m…®geima, God amozim amadaz…®ma a zaghir…®, ez…® dagheba uam azenibar aghui. 
\s1 Gumazim guiz…®n tuavim ateght…®, e uam a inigh izam 
\p  
\v 19-20 Nan adarasi, ian tav guiz…®n akam…®n tuavim ategh pura akar igharazim…®n g…®n mangam, eght…® ian tav uam a inigh iz…® guiz…®n akam…®n tuavim dat…®gham, gumazir kam arazir bar aghuim gami. Ia akar kam deragh a g…®n…®ghn…®gh! Ian tav gumazir arazir kurabagh amim…®n akuraght…®ma a tuavir kuram ategh ua God bagh izegham, gumazir kam, an arazir kurabagh amir gumazim…®n duam…®n akuraght…®ma an aremeghan kogham. Eght…® arazir kamra God arazir kurar av…®riba g…®n amadagham.\f + \ft (5:20) Marazi ghaze, Krais…®n g…®n zuir darazi, men marazi God…®n guiz…®n akam ataki. Ez…® Jems men arazibar k…®rasa, ak…®nafarir kam osiri.\f*